name: VIDEO: County Adding Mobile Offices to Deliver Services
description: A brand-new County of San Diego Live Well Mobile Office hit the road today, the second of its kind. They travel around the region and are equipped to deliver a wide range of county services directly to your community.

affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office

articleContent:
A brand-new County of San Diego Live Well Mobile Office hit the road today, the second of its kind. They travel around the region and are equipped to deliver a wide range of county services directly to your community.
See schedule or request a visit.
You can also follow the Live Well on Wheels Twitter.
